            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENumbers%2024%3A1-25%3A18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_1%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENumbers%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EBy%20now%20Balaam%20realized%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20determined%20to%20bless%20Israel%2C%20so%20he%20did%20not%20resort%20to%20divination%20as%20before.%20Instead%2C%20he%20turned%20and%20looked%20out%20toward%20the%20wilderness%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_2%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhere%20he%20saw%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20camped%2C%20tribe%20by%20tribe.%20Then%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%20came%20upon%20him%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_3%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20this%20is%20the%20message%20he%20delivered%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20the%20message%20of%20Balaam%20son%20of%20Beor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20message%20of%20the%20man%20whose%20eyes%20see%20clearly%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_4%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20message%20of%20one%20who%20hears%20the%20words%20of%20God%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20sees%20a%20vision%20from%20the%20Almighty%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20bows%20down%20with%20eyes%20wide%20open%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_5%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHow%20beautiful%20are%20your%20tents%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BJacob%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehow%20lovely%20are%20your%20homes%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BIsrael!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_6%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20spread%20before%20me%20like%20palm%20groves%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E24%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Elike%20a%20majestic%20valley.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20gardens%20by%20the%20riverside.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20are%20like%20tall%20trees%20planted%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20cedars%20beside%20the%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_7%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWater%20will%20flow%20from%20their%20buckets%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Etheir%20offspring%20have%20all%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETheir%20king%20will%20be%20greater%20than%20Agag%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Etheir%20kingdom%20will%20be%20exalted.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_24_8%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EGod%20brought%20them%20out%20of%20Egypt%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20them%20he%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20a%20wild%20ox.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E